quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  22,73,"Enywe Abandu! Mukhupilwa amachelasio, kho karechelesie. Toto balia abamulamanga abalali Nyasaye tawe shibalinyala okhuloonga kata isi tawe, kata nibekhunga’sia khulwa likhuwa elo. Ne kata isi nibanuula eshindu, shibanyala okhushikalusia okhurula khuyo tawe. Ni omuteshele muno ukhaabanga nende ukhaabungwa."
  22,74,"Shibahelesinjia Nyasaye oluyali shingala kenyekhana tawe. Toto Nyasaye ni wa Amaani, Owokhushila."
  22,75,"Nyasaye alobolanga Abarumwa Mubamalaika nende Mubandu. Toto Nyasaye niwokhuwulila muno, Owokhulola obulai po."
  22,76,"Amanyile akali imbeli wabu nende akali inyuma wabu, ne ni ewa Nyasaye wa amakhuwa koosi kalikalusibwa."
  22,77,"Enywe abasuubila, iname, ne re hasi obwenu bwenyu, ne laame Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, ne khole amalayi, mwakhaba murio mwanyoola okhubura."
  22,78,"Ne mukhalabanile Nyasaye shingala kenyekhana okhumukhalabanila. Ye niye owabaawula. Ne shiyabahelesia amakhuwa amasiro mudini tawe. Emilukha chia papa wenyu Ibrahim, niye wabalanga Abasalamu khale awo, nende mu Kurani muno mwesi mwalangwamo murio, kho Omurumwa abe omuloli khwinywe, nanyu mube abaloli khubandu. Kho, lumilile okhulaama, ne rusie eshihanwa shia Izakaa, ne tiile Nyasaye naamani muno. Ye niye Omwami wenyu. Ne ni Omwami omulayi muno uli arie uno! Ne ni omukhoonyi omulayi muno uli arie!"